Membosankan, tapi menyenangkan?

75
00:09:11,060 --> 00:09:12,190
Ya.

76
00:09:12,859 --> 00:09:13,959
Benar.

77
00:09:14,930 --> 00:09:17,200
Seperti itulah hidup sendirian.

78
