113
00:11:25,060 --> 00:11:26,119
Jang Hyun.

114
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:29,530
Hai, Se Jin.

115
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:46,739
Yoo Young.

116
00:11:47,509 --> 00:11:48,509
Ya?

117
00:11:49,979 --> 00:11:51,219
Apa kamu bahagia?

118
00:11:53,050 --> 00:11:54,249
Ya.

119
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,790
Jadi, Jang Hyun

120
00:11:56,959 --> 00:11:58,060
takut

121
00:11:59,290 --> 00:12:01,290
kehilanganmu dan melepasmu

122
00:12:01,859 --> 00:12:03,829
