132
00:12:36,589 --> 00:12:38,459
- Tentu saja!
- Hei, Teman-teman!

133
00:12:38,530 --> 00:12:39,599
Kita harus ke mana berikutnya?

134
00:12:39,660 --> 00:12:41,070
