Sesekali aku memikirkanmu.

142
00:13:08,629 --> 00:13:09,790
Aku ingat kamu.

143
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:11,660
Baik.

144
00:13:12,959 --> 00:13:14,070
Aku ingin tahu

145
00:13:14,499 --> 00:13:15,829
bagaimana bocah

146
00:13:16,530 --> 00:13:18,999
